1. Install required gems (minitest)

    bundle install

2. Run the tests

    rake

3a. Run the robot

    ruby the_robot.rb

  Issue the program at the input e.g.

    PLACE 1,2,EAST MOVE MOVE LEFT MOVE REPORT

3b. Run the robot (execute programs from file program1.theRobot)

    ruby the_robot.rb program1.theRobot
